        {
            "title": "哈佛國際新生面對川普挑戰仍創下紀錄 中國留學生增速更高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Harvard University\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"661\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8TX2mRq7lBBACCXcZLjpQg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0088f9ea8bf998064be5fa2352008da8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><span>Harvard University</span></figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 儘管川普政府一再試圖限制哈佛大學的學生簽證和資金，但這所常春藤學校在本學年招收的國際學生人數仍然創出了新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該校上周五公佈的數據顯示，2025年秋季入學的外國學生比例微升至28%，達到6749人。根據哈佛數據，這是至少自2002年以來的最高紀錄。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"661\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tEPDBgBEC9nslwU13aCDMQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c48e720f67302e7c7106eb34b01b62d0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">留學生絕對數增加了約50人，增幅不到1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">哈佛大學發言人拒絕就招生數據發表評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管中美兩國在關稅和科技等諸多問題上關係緊張，但哈佛大學的中國學生入學人數仍成長了4.5%。中國學生也是該校最大的國際生群體。韓國學生的入學人數成長了8.7%，而來自印度、英國和加拿大等國的學生人數則持平或略有下降。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-070329d2-d0b6-3602-bba7-a7f7a766b2fe-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"位於馬薩諸塞州劍橋市的哈佛大學校園。攝影：Sophie Park/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RURtJBvBEB.sEeKX4ZCe6Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2a1cb7ddf52c70bac30d0de20198d320\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">位於馬薩諸塞州劍橋市的哈佛大學校園。攝影：Sophie Park/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Harvard’s Foreign Enrollment Hits Record Despite Trump Battle</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0%E4%BB%8D%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%8B%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E6%9B%B4%E9%AB%98-224449367.html",
